Looking after elderly parents can be difficult at the best of times
A security guard from China has touched hearts across the country because he takes his 84-year-old mother with him to work on the back of his motorbike every single day
Lu Xincai takes his 84-year-old mother to work with him on the back of his motorbike every day
Mr Lu said that he rides the four kilometres to work slowly to make sure his mother feels safe and so that they can chat along the way
His elderly mother suffers from Alzheimer 's and used to get lost when she was left alone
